            <tr style="background: #f5f9f7;"><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">Skruf Fresh Mint S3</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">€2.34</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">5–6</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">€0.78–0.94</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">€23.40–28.20</td></tr>
            <tr><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">SNOBERG Double Mint</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">€1.19</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">5–6</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">€0.40–0.48</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">€11.90–14.40</td></tr>
            <tr style="background: #f5f9f7;"><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">FOLD Menthol Extreme</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">€0.89</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">3–4</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">€0.18–0.24</td><td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">€5.34–7.20</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <p><strong>Summary:</strong> Premium all-day slims cost €0.78–1.22 per day. Budget options drop to €0.18–0.48 daily. Annually: premium = €284–446; budget = €66–176.</p>

    <h2>Protecting Your Gum Health During All-Day Use</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Rotate pouch placement</strong> across all five gum areas</li>
        <li><strong>Rotate brands and flavours</strong> week-to-week</li>
        <li><strong>Limit wear time</strong> to 40–50 minutes maximum per pouch</li>
        <li><strong>Take pouch-free breaks</strong> at least 1–2 hours daily</li>
        <li><strong>Brush and floss gently</strong> twice daily with soft-bristle brush</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For comprehensive health and safety information, see our <a href="/blog/nicotine-pouch-side-effects">side effects guide</a>.</p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>What strength nicotine pouch is best for all-day use?</h3>
    <p>Lower strengths (4–8 mg) are generally better. New all-day users should start with 4–6 mg, experienced users can opt for 8–10 mg.</p>

    <h3>How many pouches should I use per day?</h3>
    <p>A typical all-day user goes through 3–6 pouches over an 8–10 hour workday. Start with 1 pouch every 2 hours and adjust.</p>

    <h3>Is slim or regular format better for all-day use?</h3>
    <p>Slim format is superior. Less jaw and gum irritation during extended wear. Mini is most discreet but delivers less nicotine per pouch.</p>

    <h3>Can I use nicotine pouches all day without gum damage?</h3>
    <p>Prolonged use can irritate gums. Minimise damage by rotating placement, rotating flavours, using lower strengths, and taking 1–2 pouch-free days per week.</p>

